1ataniq ungagivara, nipinnik qinuninniglu tusalaurngmat.
2taatsuma siutini manitimmagu uvannut,
3tuquup qilarutingita avatinnit qilaksulauqpaanga,
4tavva ataniup atinga nilliavigiliqpara:
5ataniq pitsiaqtuuvuq, isuaqtuullunilu;
6ataniup ikajuqtiksaqarunniiqtut saputiᕔt;
7tarngniik taᕾqsiqvingnut utirit;
8ataniiq tarngnira piulilauqpat tuqumit;
9pisuqullunga ataniup saangani inuujut nunanganni.
10ukpirama, tavva uqalauqpunga, “angijumik aanniatitauvunga.”
11upaluillunga uqalauqpunga, “inulimaat saglutujualuit.”
12qanuqli ataniq utiqtitsivigijunnaqparaa?
13imiut piulijauniup naluᓁkkutanga isautiniaqpara taatsumunga,
14ataniq angirutigisimajannik tunisiviginiaqpara
15ataniup takunnaqtangagut
16ataniiq ilaak pijigivarngma;
17qujalinirngmik tunirrusiviginiaqpagit
18ataniq angirutigisimajannik tunisiviginiaqpara
19ataniup iglungata itjurngᓁttuviqutingani,
